{"tid":1887304,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住14年前套法證先鋒既陣容","createTime":"2020-02-19T12:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T01:52:06.000Z","uid":155883,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c811c3ff466355017b8739be5a93ff666f40b519","tid":1887304,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"法證1 2006年<br />\n法證2 2008年<br />\n法證3 2011年<br />\n<br />\n14年前套法證真係粒粒皆星<br />\n擔大旗既歐陽警察 , 完全做到聰明, 冷靜, 機智既TIM SIR<br />\n靚仔到爆既法醫林文龍都唔錯<br />\n捧緊既鍾嘉欣 (當年先22歲咋屌) 都發揮得唔錯<br />\n<br />\n第二套基本上KEEP 到原有陣容<br />\n鍾嘉欣冇期只可以客串<br />\n但加入左鄭嘉穎, 余詩曼<br />\n整體黎講都唔差過第一部<br />\n<br />\n第三部雖然換哂血<br />\n但視帝祥配張可頤 (本身個角色係余詩曼做)<br />\n點計都算係星, 撐到成個台<br />\n<br />\n但去到第四部<br />\n竟然會係李施嬅黃浩賢呢啲人做<br />\n黃浩賢點計都比唔到歐陽警察<br />\n李施嬅同張可頤比?<br />\n仲有狄龍兒子.. 唉真係冇眼睇"},{"pid":"8763ca87d6b59b4067c022708ff0e09d2880fb83","tid":1887304,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:23:09.000Z","msg":"死肥波不了"},{"pid":"c0c8ccdea169bb72f99047264700d183fcf12f9a","tid":1887304,"uid":87757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"余詩曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879961cace3951a355a59fc2e11d09aa9f8aaf89","tid":1887304,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0c8ccdea169bb72f99047264700d183fcf12f9a","tid":1887304,"uid":87757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"余詩曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"好正, 第二輯第一幕 著 party dress"},{"pid":"93a790d8d3208c372e8fb1aa715e5d1aaed34af9","tid":1887304,"uid":168522,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"14年前黑警都冇依家咁黑"},{"pid":"6d954186311cdef768b942d61b754811fdba6fcf","tid":1887304,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"